_sText:
Second Public Build

This is a public release of the first in a series of 5 Maps designed for the Gun Game: Tournament currently in Development. You can see and download the mod here: http://www.cagemonkey.org/forum/viewtopic.php?f=6&t=245 This release is strictly to receive feedback from as many people as possible on the map itself. Please provide thoughts on: Layout Size Performance Gameplay Any and all suggestions are to be forwarded to any of these locations. Websites: Official Site: HTTP://www.cagemonkey.org/forum/ Lost's FPSB Profile: http://www.fpsbanana.com/members/109641 01 Specific Map thread:http://www.fpsbanana.com/threads/90812 Emails: Ghost.In.The.Crowd@gmail.com Logan.Dougall@gmail.com
